{"tid":1423941,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實雷射槍真係高攻擊性武器黎。。。","createTime":"2019-08-06T15:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T15:21:00.000Z","uid":17721,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"48ad36ca7adb431db8bc80a13c39ee87a5162c48","tid":1423941,"uid":17721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:08:13.000Z","msg":"雷射槍<br />\n<br />\n配把光劍，還不如配把雷射槍！──韓‧索羅，《新的希望》<br />\n<br />\n雷射槍是一款能量武器。它在銀河系裏被廣泛的使用。雷射槍的射程，手槍約五十至一百公尺餘，步槍則有三百公尺，主力艦的雷射砲視等級從數十公里到數百公里都有。大多數步兵以雷射槍為主要武器。<br />\n<br />\n運作原理 <br />\n個人雷射槍有兩種彈藥：瓦斯盒和抽取式能源匣(彈匣)。當使用者扣下板機後，高活性的雷射槍瓦斯（gas）進入轉換室（conversion enabler），彈匣便會提供能量能源瓦斯激發成高溫等離子體[1]。激發的瓦斯會通過雷射槍的驅動單元（actuating module），變成微小的高強度粒子束（intense particle beam）。然後,一個水晶稜鏡（prismatic crystal）會將粒子聚束焦。粒子聚束焦焦後，便會產生出具殺傷力的光基能源彈。<br />\n<br />\n歷史 <br />\n太野蠻了──歐比旺‧肯諾比在以雷射槍殺死格里弗斯將軍後說<br />\n<br />\n隨着銀河帝國的崛起，雷射槍成為最常見的個人武器。雷射槍不僅被軍事人員使用，還作為平民自護武器。他們是較常出現銀河系的外邊緣。<br />\n<br />\n銀河中最大的雷射槍製造商是爆擊科技(BlasTech)，在銀河內戰期間它同時向帝國軍和反抗軍出售武器。<br />\n<br />\n雷射槍類別 <br />\n雷射手槍<br />\n雷射步槍<br />\n雷射卡賓槍<br />\n連發雷射槍<br />\n雷射砲<br />\n<br />\n反制手段 <br />\n於雷射武器的普及化，偏導護盾（deflector shields）與雷射防禦裝甲（laser-proof armor）等裝置也紛紛成為反制的最佳措施。一般的步兵及地面載具限於成本、效率和實用化問題，只會配備一層裝甲。而太空中作戰的船隻最常用的防禦手段便是護盾，基本原理也是藉着建立在被保護者四周的能源力場，消耗性地抵消其他能源武器的射擊，避免雷射進一步打穿船身的裝甲。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">偏導護盾（deflector shields）與雷射防禦裝甲（laser-proof armor）係可以反制雷射槍的 請警方快速購入 免得被暴徒的雷射槍攻擊 保護自己！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<a href=\"https://starwars.fandom.com/zh/wiki/%E9%9B%B7%E5%B0%84%E6%A7%8D?variant=zh-hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstarwars.fandom.com%2Fzh%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%259B%25B7%25E5%25B0%2584%25E6%25A7%258D%3Fvariant%3Dzh-hk&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2Bv%2BaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=4a0818d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://starwars.fandom.com/zh/wiki/%E9%9B%B7%E5%B0%84%E6%A7%8D?variant=zh-hk</a>"},{"pid":"c2c494359158dd98079ad92bab9ff548ff3067a3","tid":1423941,"uid":17721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:10:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33635c68869b017bd5489fc1c296766b07f5af48","tid":1423941,"uid":17721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:10:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f902c74e10db81fcb70e21e05885942663ae21","tid":1423941,"uid":17721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:11:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2512240c7528e4523bc5db6e054712d444f66448","tid":1423941,"uid":17721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b182bdb5e16a8186aa2464532c30a0b03eec20d","tid":1423941,"uid":17721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d2260fd0dd5ae3734aca8f4f681e8a4675b0aca","tid":1423941,"uid":17721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:14:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid